<p>The XSLTProcessor transforms an XML stream into an HTML stream that can be viewed using a BrowserUI actor.</p>

<p>The actor performs the transformation using an XSLT file, which specifies how the document should be transformed. For more information about XSLT, see http://www.w3.org/TR/xslt.</p>

<p>The actor receives an XML stream via its input port. Specify an XSLT file in the XSLTFilePath parameter. The actor outputs the transformed file as a string that can be displayed by the BrowserUI actor.
 </p>

